alHealth", "GroupTherapy"], "long_description": "# Revolutionizing Group Therapy with Neao\n\nNeao's cutting-edge VR platform transforms the way therapy is delivered, fostering genuine connections and personal growth in immersive environments. We set a new standard for mental health support, enhancing both group therapy and individual sessions.\n\n**Unlock Potential in Every Session:** Immerse participants in supportive, virtual spaces that encourage authentic communication and healing, enabling individuals to connect and thrive.\n\n**Empower Therapists and Participants:** With realistic simulations and personalized programs, Neao equips therapists with tools for impactful sessions, while participants benefit from a deeply engaging experience.\n\n**Enhance Remote Therapy:** Facilitate remote sessions in VR spaces that foster strong emotional connections, regardless of physical distance.\n\n**Data-Driven Insights:** Our platform offers analytics that provide therapists with actionable insights to tailor treatment to individual needs.\n\n**Accessible VR for Mental Health:** Neao\u2019s solutions revolutionize therapy, offering a more effective alternative to traditional methods.\n\n**Join Neao:** Explore how Neao's VR solutions can reshape therapy, driving better outcomes for both therapists and clients.", "short_description": "Neao is a pioneering platform delivering end-to-end VR solutions for group therapy. Our immersive VR platform with unique treatment programs creates a powerful tool for therapists and empowers individuals to connect, grow, and heal in safe and supportive virtual environments."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://neao.io/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Foretell Reality", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://neao.io/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_ca